quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  20,99,is terhan par hum tum se woh halaat bayan karte hain jo guzar chuke hain. aur hum ne tumhe apne paas se nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) ataa farmai hai
  20,100,jo shakhs is se munh phairay ga woh qayamat ke din ( gunah ka ) boojh uthaiye ga
  20,101,( aisay log ) hamesha is ( azaab ) mein ( mubtala ) rahen ge aur yeh boojh qayamat ke roz un ke liye bura hai
  20,102,jis roz sor phonka jaye ga aur hum gunahgaaron ko akatha karen ge aur un ki ankhen niilii niilii hon gi
  20,103,( to ) woh aapas mein aahista aahista kahin ge ke tum ( duniya mein ) sirf das hi din rahay ho
  20,104,jo baatein yeh karen ge hum khoob jantay hain. is waqt un mein sab se achi raah wala ( yani Aqil وہوشمند ) kahe ga ke ( nahi balkay ) sirf aik hi roz thehray ho
  20,105,aur tum se pahoron ke baray mein daryaft karte hain. keh do ke khuda un ko urra kar bekhair day ga
  20,106,aur zameen ko hamwar maidan kar chhorey ga
  20,107,jis mein nah tum kajji ( aur pasti ) dekho ge nah teela ( aur bulandi )
  20,108,is roz log aik pukarnay walay ke peechay chalein ge aur is ki pairwi se inhiraf nah kar saken ge aur khuda ke samnay aawazian pust ho jaien gi to tum aawaz khfi ke siwa koi aawaz nah suno ge
  20,109,is roz ( kisi ki ) sifarish kuch faida nah day gi magar is shakhs ki jisay khuda ijazat day aur is ki baat ko pasand farmaiye
  20,110,jo kuch un ke agay hai aur kuch un ke peechay hai woh is ko jaanta hai aur woh ( apne ) ilm se khuda ( ke ilm ) par ihata nahi kar saktay
  20,111,aur is zindah o qaim ke ro baroo munh neechay ho jaien ge. aur jis ne zulm ka boojh uthaya woh namuraad raha
  20,112,aur jo naik kaam kere ga aur momin bhi hoga to is ko nah zulm ka khauf hoga aur nah nuqsaan ka
  20,113,aur hum ne is ko isi terhan ka quran arabi nazilkiya hai aur is mein terhan terhan ke draway bayan kardiye hain taakay log parhaizgaar banin ya khuda un ke liye nasiyaat peda kardey
